     C/EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRINIT - Subroutine to do Program Initialisation.            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  Main Processing                                  *
      *  Calls    :  *PSSR  - Error Control Subroutine                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRINIT    BEGSR                           *** SRINIT ***
      *
      **  Set up copyright parameter
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      CPY2@  80
      *
      **  Receive Parameter List.
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PSEQN   5
     C                     PARM           PLEVL   1
     C                     PARM           PENTY   3
      *
      **  Initialise LDA field.
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           LDA
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'XX0541'  DBPGM
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   DBKEY
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   DBFILE
     C                     Z-ADD*ZEROS    DBASE
     C                     OUT  LDA
      *
      **  Call Access Program for Bank Details - Title, Run Date,
      **  Run Day Number and Base Currency
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOBANKR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*FIRST ' POPTN   7
     C           SDBANK    PARM SDBANK    DSFDY
      *
      **  Handle Database Error.
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'SDBANKPD'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     Z-ADD1         DBASE            * DB ERROR 01 *
     C                     MOVEL'*FIRST'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Call Access Program for Currency Details - Base Currency
      **  decimal places.
      *
     C                     CALL 'AOCURRR0'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD
     C                     PARM '*KEY   ' POPTN
     C                     PARM BJCYCD    PCCY    3
     C********** SDCURR    PARM SDCURR    DSFDY                                 CSD006
     C           SDCURR    PARM SDCURR    DSSDY                                 CSD006
      *
      **  Handle Database Error.
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'SDCURRPD'DBFILE           ************
     C                     Z-ADD4         DBASE            * DBERR 04 *
     C                     MOVELPCCY      DBKEY            ************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDA6NBDP    BCNBDP  10
      *
      **   Access RUNDAT for multibranching indicator
      *
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           RUNDAT
     C                     IN   RUNDAT
      *
     C           AGMBIN    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN37
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN37
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  System level requested.
      *
     C           PLEVL     IFEQ 'S'
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN38
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Check if feature FVT102 is present.                                                 FVT102
      *                                                                                       FVT102
     C                     MOVE 'N'       FVT102  1                                           FVT102
     C                     CALL 'AOSARDR0'                                                    FVT102
     C                     PARM '       ' @RTCD   7                                           FVT102
     C                     PARM '*VERIFY' @OPTN   7                                           FVT102
     C                     PARM 'FVT102'  @SARD   6                                           FVT102
     C           SCSARD    PARM SCSARD    DSFDY                                               FVT102
     C*                                                                                       FVT102
     C           @RTCD     IFEQ *BLANKS                                                       FVT102
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       FVT102                                              FVT102
     C                     ENDIF                                                              FVT102
      *                                                                                       FVT102
      **  Initialise Report Work fields.
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         RQDLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         DIFLN1  30
     C                     Z-ADD0         WRCNT   50
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         WSPEQ  150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTSPT  150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTBCE  150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTSPV  150
     C                     Z-ADD0         WTPLO  150
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WOPEN   1
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRPROC
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRPROC - Subroutine to Process Spot Revaluations             *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  Main Processing                                  *
      *  Calls    :  SRNWBR - Process New Branch                      *
      *              SRLINE - Check Remaining Lines on Page           *
      *              SRCHBR - Process a Change in Branch              *
      *              SRTOTL - Print a Subtotal Line                   *
      *              *PSSR  - Error Control Subroutine                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRPROC    BEGSR                           *** SRPROC ***
      *
      **  Process New Branch
      *
     C                     EXSR SRNWBR
      *
      **  Do While Not End of File.
      *
     C           *IN89     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
      **  Save current branch and current currency details
      *
     C                     MOVE SRBRCD    WSVBR   3
     C                     MOVE SRCYCD    WSVCY   3
     C                     MOVE SRCYNM    WSVNM  14
     C                     Z-ADDSRNBDP    WNBDP   10
     C                     Z-ADDSRSPRT    WSVRT  138
      *
      **  Call GL0765 to convert the Period End Balance into Base Ccy
      *
     C                     CALL 'GL0765'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM SRCYCD    PCYCD   3
     C                     PARM BJCYCD    PBCCY   3
     C                     PARM 99999     PDYNB   50
     C           WSPEQ     PARM SREPCB    PAMNT  190
      *
      **  Handle database error
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANKS
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'See Dump'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     Z-ADD2         DBASE            * DB ERROR 02 *
     C                     MOVEL'GL0765'  DBKEY            ***************
     C                     OUT  LDA
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Compute for 'Revaluation P&L'
      *
     C           SRBCEQ    SUB  WSPEQ     WRVPL  150
      *
      **  Accumulate closing balance, base ccy equivalent, spot trade
      **  equivalent, and revaluation P&L.
      *
     C                     ADD  SREPCB    WTSPT
     C                     ADD  SRBCEQ    WTBCE
     C                     ADD  WSPEQ     WTSPV
     C                     ADD  WRVPL     WTPLO
      *
      **  Setup report details
      *
     C                     MOVE SRPCCD    RPRFC
     C                     MOVE SRBKCD    RBKCD
     C                     MOVE SROTTP    ROTTP
     C                     MOVE SRTSTY    RTSTY
     C           SRASNB    IFEQ *ZERO
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   RASNB
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE SRASNB    RASNB
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Format Spot Position/Closing Balance
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSREPCB    ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADDSRNBDP    ZDECS
     C                     MOVE 'A'       ZECODE
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RSPOT
      *
      **  Format Base Currency Equivalent
      *
     C                     Z-ADDSRBCEQ    ZFLD15
     C                     Z-ADDBCNBDP    ZDECS
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RBCEQ
      *
      **  Format Spot Value/Spot Trade Equivalent
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWSPEQ     ZFLD15
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RSPVL
      *
      **  Format Revaluation Profit/Loss
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWRVPL     ZFLD15
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RPRLO
      *
      **  Check that sufficient lines remain for the Format
      *
     C                     Z-ADD6         RQDLN1
     C                     EXSR SRLINE
      *
      **  Write out Detail Record and add 1 to currency record count.
      *
     C                     WRITEDETAIL
     C                     ADD  1         WRCNT   50
      *
      **  Read next record.
      *
     C                     READ MCSRRPOQ                 89
      *
      **  If End of File or Change of Branch
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *ON
     C           SRBRCD    ORNE RBRCH
     C                     EXSR SRCHBR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  If Not End of File and Change of Currency
      *
     C           *IN89     IFEQ *OFF
     C           SRCYCD    ANDNERCYCD
     C                     EXSR SRCHCY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  End of Do While Not End of Valid Records.
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRNWBR
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRNWBR - Subroutine to Process New Branch                    *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called By:  SRPROC - Process Detail Line                     *
      *              SRCHBR - Process a Change in Branch              *
      *  Calls    :  SRRCFP - RCF Processing for P1                   *
      *              SRLINE - Check Remaining Lines on Page           *
      *              *PSSR - Database Error Handling Subroutine       *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
      *
     C           SRNWBR    BEGSR                           *** SRNWBR ***
      *
      **  Get branch details using access object
      *
     C**********           CALL 'AOBRCHR0'                                                    CGL029
     C                     CALL 'AOBRCHR1'                                                    CGL029
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   PRTCD   7
     C                     PARM '*KEY    'POPTN   7
     C                     PARM SRBRCD    PBRCA   3
     C********** SDBRCH    PARM SDBRCH    DSFDY                                               CGL029
     C           SDBRCH    PARM SDBRCH    DSSDY                                               CGL029
      *
      **  Handle database error
      *
     C           PRTCD     IFNE *BLANK
     C           *LOCK     IN   LDA
     C                     MOVEL'SDBRCHPD'DBFILE           ***************
     C                     MOVELPBRCA     DBKEY            * DB ERROR 03 *
     C                     Z-ADD3         DBASE            ***************
     C                     EXSR *PSSR
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVELA8BRCD    RBRCH
     C                     MOVELA8BRNM    RBRNM
      *
      **  Open printer file XX0541P1 if entity not blank
      **  or the printer file is not yet open
      *
     C           PENTY     IFNE *BLANK
     C           WOPEN     ORNE 'Y'
     C                     OPEN XX0541P1
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WOPEN
      *
      **  Ensure Report Spool File recorded by RCF
      *
     C           PENTY     IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVE SRBRCD    SENTY
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   SENTY
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     EXSR SRRCFP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      **  Check remaining lines on page
      *
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       WCHCY   1
     C                     Z-ADD99        RQDLN1
     C                     EXSR SRLINE
     C                     MOVE 'N'       WCHCY
      *
     C                     ENDSR
      *****************************************************************
      /TITLE SR/SRHEAD                                                                        FVT102
      *****************************************************************                       FVT102
