      *
      **  Format Total Spot Value/Spot Trade Equivalent
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWTSPV     ZFLD15
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RTSPV
      *
      **  Format Total Revaluation Profit/Loss
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWTPLO     ZFLD15
     C                     EXSR ZFRPED
     C                     MOVE ZOUT22    RTPLO
      *
